global-fap.description:
We only use premium quality heavyweight (200gsm) fine art print material with a smooth, clean matt finish. All prints by Pixy Paper are made using state-of-the-art digital giclée printers. With a vibrant and clean design, your print will last a lifetime.

We are very proud that our prints are eco-friendly; they contain no plastic, are made using water based inks and sustainably sourced paper.

All sizes displayed are in inches, for more information on sizes please visit our size guide page.
